{"tid":1933543,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國戲| 2020 就愛斷捨離 Happy old year 預吿片","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T05:51:58.000Z","uid":69460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"befeff61b88474fa42d1e84b642779150662246a","tid":1933543,"uid":69460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.marieclaire.com.tw/entertainment/movie/A46823/happy-old-year-movie\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marieclaire.com.tw%2Fentertainment%2Fmovie%2FA46823%2Fhappy-old-year-movie&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=89db4cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.marieclaire.com.tw/entertainment/movie/A46823/happy-old-year-movie</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/natalie0609/1581316919-4231752920_wn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fnatalie0609%2F1581316919-4231752920_wn.jpg&h=2a82a953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信各位常常聽到「斷捨離」，不需要的東西就趕快丟了，才能迎接新的事物。不過這部2020年泰國新片《就愛斷捨離 Happy Old Year》卻讓人難以果斷割捨的，則是回憶能夠說丟就丟嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ojH_f6DNRyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FojH_f6DNRyc&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=201d085f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ojH_f6DNRyc</a><br />\n<br />\n淨睇預告片巳經眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n導演上一套較知名嘅2015 heart attack 戀愛診療中 <br />\n應該幾多人睇過  <br />\n男主角上一套短髮光頭成個傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次長髮留鬚變咗男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢套文藝feel幾重但都好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0df53362c57462b85f67d519f38b3ad221fb9e","tid":1933543,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco